&lt;h2 id=&#34;b2u2&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;markdownIt-Anchor&#34; href=&#34;#b2u2&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; B2U2&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;每年数以百万计的高校毕业生涌向就业市场，就业压力巨大。但另一方面互联网浪潮正将年轻人推向时代的最前沿。在中国，已有不少年轻人选择借助网络优势实现自己的创业梦想。相比于传统的创业模式，借助互联网创业成本较少、门槛较低，只要肯努力、有技术，好点子就很有可能变为真金子。因此，互联网对于创业青年来说意味着更多机遇。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reference:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;University graduates face high employment pressure with millions of them swarming into the job markdet every year. On the other hand, the Internet tide is thrusting them to the fore of the era. In China, many young people choose to realize their entrepreneurial dreams by taking advantage of the Internet. Compared with traditional entrepreneurial models, launching an online business needs less money and has easier entry. As long as one is willing to work hard and knows the necessary technology, a good idea has the largest chance of turning into real money. Therefore, the Internet means more opportunities for  those young people who want to start their own business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;b2u3&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;markdownIt-Anchor&#34; href=&#34;#b2u3&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; B2U3:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;领导力就是促使人们做到最好，帮助他们最大限度地发掘潜力，激励他们为共同目标而努力。领导者要在恰当的时机办好该办的事。优秀的、卓有成效的领导者都会尊重他人。尊重他人的领导者会发现自己也会得到别人的尊重。所有相关人员都会受到激励而共同努力。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reference:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Leadership is all about getting people to give their best, helping them to grow their fullest potential, and motivating them to work toward a common goal. Leaders make the right things happen when they’re supposed to. A good leader, and effective leader is one who has respect for others. A leader who has respec for other people will find that respect is returned. And all concerned will be motivated to work together.&lt;/p&gt;
